<p>This webinar provides an overview of basic information required to successfully manage your Rural grant and include topics such as special conditions, training and technical assistance, OVW TA vs. Non-sponsored OVW TA, grant adjustment notices and submission, types of GANs, deliverables, reports, and closeout.</p>
