<h3>Using the Grants Management System (GMS) to Manage your OVW Award</h3>
<b>December 19, 2014</b>
<p><b>Presenters:</b> Kyle Lohrke, Office on Violence Against Women, U.S. Department of Justice</p>
<p>This webinar is an overview of the Grants Management System (GMS) and how grantees use it to submit Grant Adjustment Notices (GANs) and grant reports and make other formal changes to their awards. Program and financial points-of-contact who are new to using GMS should participate.</p>
