<p>This webinar is intended to help OVW grantees manage their OVW awards in accordance with the OVW Grants Financial Management Guide and other applicable rules and regulations. A question and answer (Q&A) session will follow the presentation. Program and financial points-of-contact who are: a) new to managing OVW awards; and/or b) received an FY 2014 OVW award and will not be attending an in-person grantee orientation should participate.</p>
